──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  [evolve] missing capability: 'arithmetic-add'
  [evolve] proposed: ⊕ add — Value + Value → Number
  [ipfs] evolved alphabet pinned as shp-9ca349bd440afd45
         delta: +1 verb (⊕ add), 10 → 11
         language version chain: shp-4c6ab48969be3777 → shp-9ca349bd440afd45

──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
